---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="JellyJam 2026 | Underwater Game Jam">
  <section class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-4 relative pt-20 pb-20">
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-jelly-blue/20 blur-[120px] -z-10 animate-pulse"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-jelly-pink/15 blur-[120px] -z-10 animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 1s;"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-80 h-80 bg-cyan-400/10 blur-[100px] -z-10 animate-wave"></div>
    
    <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black italic mt-8 mb-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-jelly-blue via-white to-jelly-pink bg-clip-text text-transparent leading-tight font-display tracking-tighter cursor-default select-none">âœ¨ Jellyfish Jam âœ¨</h1>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-blue-200/70 max-w-2xl font-light tracking-wide mb-12">A 12-hour game jam at Leland High School. Dive deep into the marine theme.</p>
    
    <div class="glass px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-jelly-blue tracking-wider hover:bg-jelly-blue/10 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(1,205,254,0.5)] active:scale-95 transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer select-none group" onclick="window.rippleElement(this)">
      <span class="inline-block group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-300">ğŸ®</span> GAME START: APRIL Something, 2026
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="card" onclick="window.rippleElement(this)">
    <h3>The Squish</h3>
    <p>Click me to make a splash!</p>
  </div>
  <!-- About: Three features section -->
  <section id="about" class="max-w-6xl mx-auto py-40 px-6">
    <!-- Section Title -->
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black font-display tracking-tighter text-jelly-pink mb-0">
        About JellyJam
      </h2>
      <p class="text-blue-200/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        A squishy, creative game jam where indie devs dive into ocean-inspired ideas together.
      </p>
    </div>
  
    <!-- Cards Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="card group-hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(255,113,206,0.3)]">
        <div class="text-jelly-pink text-6xl mb-8 font-black tracking-tighter font-display group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-3 transition-transform duration-300 origin-left">ğŸŒŠ</div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display mb-4 group-hover:text-jelly-pink transition-colors duration-300">The Squish</h3>
        <p class="text-blue-200/60 leading-relaxed group-hover:text-blue-200/80 transition-colors duration-300">
          Flow together with a community of indie devs. Create games that feel fluid and fun. All skill levels welcome in our ocean!
        </p>
      </div>
  
      <div class="card group-hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(1,205,254,0.3)]">
        <div class="text-jelly-blue text-6xl mb-8 font-black tracking-tighter font-display group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:-rotate-3 transition-transform duration-300 origin-left">ğŸ™</div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display mb-4 group-hover:text-jelly-blue transition-colors duration-300">The Theme</h3>
        <p class="text-blue-200/60 leading-relaxed group-hover:text-blue-200/80 transition-colors duration-300">
          Dive into "Marine". Interpret it mechanically, narratively, or visually. Jellies included, but let your creativity swim free!
        </p>
      </div>
  
      <div class="card group-hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(255,113,206,0.3)]">
        <div class="text-jelly-pink text-6xl mb-8 font-black tracking-tighter font-display group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-3 transition-transform duration-300 origin-left">ğŸ†</div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display mb-4 group-hover:text-jelly-pink transition-colors duration-300">The Loot</h3>
        <p class="text-blue-200/60 leading-relaxed group-hover:text-blue-200/80 transition-colors duration-300">
          Top games get surfaced on this website and win some prizes! Rising stars of the game jam ocean!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section id="sponsors" class="py-28 border-y border-white/10">
    <p class="text-center text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-16 opacity-60 font-semibold">ğŸŒŠ Currents of Support ğŸŒŠ</p>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-12 grayscale opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300">
      <img src="/logos/unity.svg" alt="Sponsor" class="h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform" />
      <img src="/logos/github.svg" alt="Sponsor" class="h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform" />
      <img src="/logos/pico8.svg" alt="Sponsor" class="h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform" />
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section id="rules" class="py-40 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-jelly-blue/5 to-transparent">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mb-4 text-center italic font-display">ğŸ¤ Water Rules</h2>
        <p class="text-blue-200/70 text-lg font-light">Keep our ocean clean and kind.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="rule-item group-hover:shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(255,113,206,0.2)]">
          <div class="rule-bullet bg-jelly-pink shadow-[0_0_15px_#ff71ce]"></div>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-blue-200/80 group-hover:text-blue-200/100 transition-colors duration-300"><span class="font-semibold text-white">"Fresh Water Only":</span> All code and assets must be made during the jam or be CC0. Keep it clean!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rule-item group-hover:shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(1,205,254,0.2)]">
          <div class="rule-bullet bg-jelly-blue shadow-[0_0_15px_#01cdfe]"></div>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-blue-200/80 group-hover:text-blue-200/100 transition-colors duration-300"><span class="font-semibold text-white">"Don't Sting":</span> Be kind and supportive. Our ocean is friendliest when we lift each other up.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section id="location" class="py-40">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-20">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black italic mb-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-jelly-blue to-jelly-pink bg-clip-text text-transparent font-display">ğŸ—ºï¸ Global Currents</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-blue-200/70 mb-12 leading-relaxed hover:text-blue-200/90 transition-colors duration-300">
          JellyJam 2026 is a <span class="font-semibold text-white">fully virtual ocean</span>, streaming live from our underwater studio in Tokyo, JP.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="glass p-6 rounded-2xl flex items-center gap-4 hover:bg-white/12 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(1,205,254,0.2)] hover:translate-x-2 transition-all duration-300 group cursor-pointer">
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-jelly-blue/20 rounded-lg font-medium text-jelly-blue text-sm group-hover:bg-jelly-blue/40 transition-colors duration-300">Platform</span>
            <span class="font-semibold group-hover:text-jelly-blue transition-colors duration-300">itch.io / Discord</span>
          </div>
          <div class="glass p-6 rounded-2xl flex items-center gap-4 hover:bg-white/12 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(1,205,254,0.2)] hover:translate-x-2 transition-all duration-300 group cursor-pointer">
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-jelly-blue/20 rounded-lg font-medium text-jelly-blue text-sm group-hover:bg-jelly-blue/40 transition-colors duration-300">Timezone</span>
            <span class="font-semibold group-hover:text-jelly-blue transition-colors duration-300">UTC-0 (Universal Time)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1 glass aspect-video rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-white/12 hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(255,113,206,0.3)] hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 group cursor-pointer">
        <div class="text-center">
          <span class="text-jelly-pink font-black text-3xl block animate-pulse group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-300">â–¶</span>
          <span class="text-jelly-pink font-semibold text-lg mt-3 block group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">LIVE STREAM FEED</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section id="team" class="max-w-6xl mx-auto py-40 px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-black italic mb-4 font-display">ğŸ™ The Tentacles</h2>
      <p class="text-blue-200/70 text-lg font-light">Meet the team making waves in the ocean.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <div class="text-center group cursor-pointer">
        <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto rounded-full bg-gradient-to-tr from-jelly-blue to-jelly-pink p-1 mb-4 group-hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(1,205,254,0.5)] group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-full h-full rounded-full bg-deep-ocean group-hover:scale-95 transition">
             <img src="https://api.dicebear.com/7.x/avataaars/svg?seed=Felix" alt="Team member" class="group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-bold font-display uppercase tracking-tighter group-hover:text-jelly-pink transition-colors duration-300\">Captain Jellyfish</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-jelly-blue font-mono group-hover:text-jelly-blue/80 transition-colors duration-300">Lead Organizer</p>
      </div>
      </div>
  </section>
  
  <section id="faq" class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-40 px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-black italic mb-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-jelly-blue to-jelly-pink bg-clip-text text-transparent font-display">ğŸŒŠ Deep Dive (FAQ)</h2>
      <p class="text-blue-200/70 text-lg font-light">Curious about how this all works? Let's answer your questions.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid gap-6">
      <details class="glass p-8 rounded-2xl group cursor-pointer hover:bg-white/12 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(1,205,254,0.25)] transition-all duration-150 open:bg-white/12\">
        <summary class="text-lg font-bold font-display list-none flex justify-between items-center text-white group-open:text-jelly-blue transition-colors duration-300 select-none">
          What even is a Game Jam?
          <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300 text-jelly-blue group-hover:scale-125 inline-block">â†“</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-5 text-blue-200/70 leading-relaxed group-open:text-blue-200/90 transition-colors duration-300">
          It's a hackathon for games! You have 12 hours to create from scratch based on our Marine theme. At the end, you submit your creation and the community rates it! Perfect for learning, experimenting, and having fun.
        </p>
      </details>
  
      <details class="glass p-8 rounded-2xl group cursor-pointer hover:bg-white/12 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(1,205,254,0.25)] transition-all duration-150 open:bg-white/12">
        <summary class="text-lg font-bold font-display list-none flex justify-between items-center text-white group-open:text-jelly-blue transition-colors duration-150 select-none">
          Do I need a team?
          <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-150 text-jelly-blue group-hover:scale-125 inline-block">â†“</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-5 text-blue-200/70 leading-relaxed group-open:text-blue-200/90 transition-colors duration-300">
          Nope! You can go solo (Lone Jelly) or form a school of fish (up to 4 members). Check our Discord to find teammates with complementary skills. Solo jellyfish welcome!
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="glass p-8 rounded-2xl group cursor-pointer hover:bg-white/12 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(1,205,254,0.25)] transition-all duration-150 open:bg-white/12">
        <summary class="text-lg font-bold font-display list-none flex justify-between items-center text-white group-open:text-jelly-blue transition-colors duration-150 select-none">
          What tools can I use?
          <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-150 text-jelly-blue group-hover:scale-125 inline-block">â†“</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-5 text-blue-200/70 leading-relaxed group-open:text-blue-200/90 transition-colors duration-300">
          Any engine, framework, or even pen & paper! Unity, Godot, Unreal, Pico-8, custom enginesâ€”wherever your creativity flows. As long as your game is playable and respects the jam rules, you're good to dive in!
        </p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>
  
</MainLayout>